      "value": "Learn spells from new Species and increase spell limit."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Requirements: </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">you must have mastered the </span><strong>Chimerist </strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Class.</span> </p></blockquote><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Choose two creature Species among </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>construct</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>demon</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>elemental</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, and </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>undead</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">. You can now use </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>spell mimic</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">to learn spells from creatures of the chosen Species. </span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">This Heroic Skill </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>may be acquired up to twice</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, each time selecting two Species from the list above.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Whenever you acquire this Skill, you also increase your upper limit for memorized Chimerist spells by 2.</span> </p>",
